        User might not realize that this activity comes directly from AnkiDroid,
        so it might be wise to avoid words such as “AnkiDroid or “app”."
        >Are you sure you want to delete all data? This includes your collection, media, backups and preferences.\n\nNote: this action will close the window.</string>

